headline: Josys Recognized in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for SaaS Management Platforms
summary: Josys, the SaaS Management Platform that simplifies how IT works, today announced its continued recognition in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for SaaS Management Platforms report.
